<h1>Gephex 0.4.2 Release Notes</h1>

<p>On January 26th, 2005, the Gephex Project released Gephex 0.4.2</p>

<p>Gephex is a modular real-time video effect framework.
0.4.2 is a bugfix and stabilization release of the 0.4 branch.
It also introduces minor feature enhancements.
</p>

